כל Alert של Kobi Auto Bot Smart

כל Alert כפול של Kobi Auto Bot Smart Risk

תשאיר רק Alert אחד של:

Kobi Auto Bot Smart Risk (40, 80)

סוג: Alert() function calls only

אם אתה רוצה גם למנוע מהקוד לשלוח יותר מדי, תחליף את הקוד לזה:

//@version=5
strategy("Kobi Auto Bot Smart Risk", overlay=true, pyramiding=0)

// Risk settings
stopLossPoints = input.int(40, "Stop Loss Points")
takeProfitPoints = input.int(80, "Take Profit Points")

// Fast averages
fast = ta.ema(close, 2)
slow = ta.ema(close, 5)

// Conditions
longCondition = ta.crossover(fast, slow)
shortCondition = ta.crossunder(fast, slow)

// Entries + alerts
if (longCondition and strategy.position_size <= 0)
    strategy.entry("BUY", strategy.long)
    alert('{"action":"BUY"}', alert.freq_once_per_bar_close)

if (shortCondition and strategy.position_size >= 0)
    strategy.entry("SELL", strategy.short)
    alert('{"action":"SELL"}', alert.freq_once_per_bar_close)

// Risk exits
strategy.exit("BUY EXIT", from_entry="BUY", profit=takeProfitPoints, loss=stopLossPoints)
strategy.exit("SELL EXIT", from_entry="SELL", profit=takeProfitPoints, loss=stopLossPoints)

// Draw
plot(fast, color=color.orange)
plot(slow, color=color.blue)
plotshape(longCondition, title="BUY", style=shape.labelup, location=location.belowbar, text="BUY")
plotshape(shortCondition, title="SELL", style=shape.labeldown, location=location.abovebar, text="SELL")
